### Test Sales API with Multiple Currencies

### 1. Get all currencies first
GET http://localhost:5000/api/core/currencies
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Get all customers
GET http://localhost:5000/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Get all products
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Create a sale in PKR
POST http://localhost:5000/api/sales/bulk-create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "saleDate": "2024-11-17T10:00:00Z",
